{
  "texts": [
    "The maximum OpenGL ES shader performance is 512 GFLOPS (FP16) with a maximum operating frequency of 921MHz.",
    "The processor is an ARM Cortex-A57 MPCore with NEON Technology (Quad-Core), with 48KB L1 instruction cache per core and 32KB L1 data cache per core.",
    "It also has a 2MB L2 Unified Cache, and its maximum operating frequency is 1.43 GHz [21].",
    "Deep learning focuses on acquiring suitable data representations to achieve desired outcomes.",
    "The term \"deep\" in deep learning signifies learning hierarchical concepts directly from raw data [22]."
